headline: Should Investors Reassess Cboe After a Five Year 207% Surge and New Regulatory Updates?
summary: If you have been weighing what to do with Cboe Global Markets stock, you are not alone. It is one of those names that always finds its way back into investor discussions, especially after a big swing in either direction. Over the past five years, shares have soared 207.1%. Even after some recent wobbles, such as a -2.2% stretch over the past month, the general trend is undeniably upward. Year to date, Cboe is up a strong 21.3%, adding to the confidence many already feel about its long-term...
